Class ItemPlaceholderComparison

  • java.lang.Object

    A representation of the differences between two versions of the same Item when one or both are only visible as ItemPlaceholders.

    2.0

        Constructs a new ItemPlaceholderComparison.
        Parameters:
        olderItem - The older Item or ItemPlaceholder in this ItemPlaceholderComparison.
        newerItem - The newer Item or ItemPlaceholder in this ItemPlaceholderComparison.
        deletionChanged - true if one of the versions is marked as deleted while the other is not; false otherwise.
        securityChanged - true if the versions have different security settings; false otherwise.
